---
// Clayy wordmark with a soft glowing orange dot.
---

<div class="group inline-flex items-center gap-2">
  <span class="font-mono font-semibold text-white text-base tracking-tight transition-colors group-hover:text-orange-500">
    Clayy
  </span>
  <span class="relative inline-flex items-center justify-center w-2 h-2">
    <span
      class="absolute inline-flex w-full h-full rounded-full bg-orange-500 opacity-70 animate-ping"
    ></span>
    <span
      class="relative inline-flex w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-orange-500 shadow-[0_0_8px_rgba(255,102,0,0.9),0_0_16px_rgba(255,102,0,0.5)]"
    ></span>
  </span>
</div>
